DEBUG: upsert_asset values: ('6783eaf5-34a0-4359-b876-5d94930d9d74', 'ce65bb2f-2c69-4493-a2c0-c68fe17aa54f', 'slide_deck', 'completed', "['Generate a 20-slide presentation based on Fenizia and Saggio (2024). STYLE: Strictly white background, no other background colors. STRUCTURE: 1. Title/Introduction, 2-3. Motivation (costs of OC), 4. Literature Review, 5. Institutional Background (CCDs), 6. Data (INPS, Treasury, ANAC), 7-10. Detailed Methodology on Matched DiD (matching algorithm, probit, econometric specification, parallel trends assumption), 11-14. Main Results (Employment, Firms, Dynamism, Real Estate Prices), 15-18. Mechanisms (Political turnover, connection breakage, Mafia sectors), 19. Robustness Tests (Shocks, Spillovers), 20. Conclusion. Use references to Figures 1-10 and Tables 1-4 from the sources. Academic and rigorous tone.', 'en', 2, 3]", None, {})
