DEBUG: upsert_asset values: ('1c41e288-db04-4612-97fb-1f4c2af2a1a0', '3d95540f-cda5-4e49-8069-3a2b4f3d19c9', 'slide_deck', 'completed', "['Create a 15-slide academic presentation in English with a white background. Use only original figures and tables from the source material. Focus exclusively on the Regression Discontinuity Design (RDD) framework. The structure must include: 1. Title/Intro, 2. Research Question/Motivation, 3. Leapfrogging model (Figure 2 panel c), 4. War on Drugs context (Figure 3), 5. Oil theft context (Figure 1), 6. RDD Strategy (Equation 4), 7. Political Alignment (Figure 4), 8. Validity: Balancing tests (Table A.9), 9. Validity: Density test (Figure A.7), 10. Validity: Placebo 2006 (Table A.10), 11. Main Results: Visual (Figure 6), 12. Main Results: Estimates (Table 3), 13. Robustness: Permutation tests (Figure A.10), 14. Robustness: Bandwidth sensitivity (Figure A.8), 15. Dynamic Effects & Policy (Figure 7).', 'en-US', None, 3]", None, {})
